sequenceDiagram
    participant K8s as Kubernetes<br/>(ConfigMap + Secret)
    participant Adapter as LMEval Adapter<br/>(main.py)
    participant LMEval as lm-evaluation-harness<br/>(lm_eval/)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over K8s,Adapter: Phase 1: Initialization
        K8s->>Adapter: Mount /meta/job.json (ConfigMap)
        K8s->>Adapter: Mount credentials (Secret)<br/>API key, HF token, CA cert
        Adapter->>Adapter: Parse JobSpec<br/>Resolve credentials
        Adapter->>Adapter: Detect offline mode<br/>(check /test_data layout)
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Adapter,HF: Phase 2: Data Loading
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        LMEval->>HF: GET datasets, tokenizers<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>LMEval: Benchmark datasets<br/>(MMLU, ARC, HellaSwag, etc.)
        Note over LMEval,HF: Skipped in offline mode<br/>(uses /test_data instead)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over LMEval,Model: Phase 3: Evaluation Execution
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        loop For each benchmark task batch
            LMEval->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Prompt batch (up to 128 concurrent)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA)
            Model-->>LMEval: Completions / logprobs
        end
        LMEval->>LMEval: Compute metrics<br/>(F1, accuracy, BLEU, etc.)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Adapter,MLflow: Phase 4: Post-Processing & Persistence
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Adapter->>Adapter: Package results as<br/>OCI artifact (olot)
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Adapter->>OCI: Push OCI artifact (skopeo)<br/>Auth: Basic auth / Docker config<br/>TLS 1.2+
        OCI-->>Adapter: Push confirmation
        Adapter->>MLflow: Log metrics & metadata<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        MLflow-->>Adapter: Log confirmation
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 248)
        Note over Adapter,EvalHub: Phase 5: Completion
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: COMPLETED<br/>Results: JSON metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Adapter,EvalHub: Error Handling (any phase)
        Adapter->>Adapter: Sanitize error message<br/>(strip Bearer tokens, API keys,<br/>URL userinfo, query params)
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: ERROR<br/>Code: e.g. model_rate_limited<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end
